Ah, that's the reason, when you have 2 factor authentication, you need to give a personal access token as the password, not the one you use to login to github.
Btw, it's easier if you use ssh protocol
git remote set-url origin git@github.com:sympy/sympy-paper this would change the protocol from https to ssh
